{"tid":2343600,"cid":5,"subCid":10,"title":"李運騰批准黎智英保釋 明午4時半頒布書面理由","createTime":"2020-12-28T05:25:10.000Z","updateTime":"2020-12-29T07:16:04.000Z","uid":240362,"like":32,"dislike":1,"uniUserReply":32,"replies":[{"pid":"8891e56c6e245400850792b06a71ce9189370f0e","tid":2343600,"uid":240362,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-12-28T05:25:10.000Z","msg":"<a href=\"https://t.me/youarenotalonehk_info/4787\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Ft.me%2Fyouarenotalonehk_info%2F4787&d=%2BrTTj2V4oNsvrkryR3gjdz%2FbAHlNv8jCBJNC2S%2BJHYY%3D&h=e34b3c97\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://t.me/youarenotalonehk_info/4787</a><br />\n<br />\n國安法官李運騰准黎智英保釋 明午4:30頒布理由<br />\n<br />\n【頭條日報】高等法院法官李運騰上周批准涉嫌違反《港區國安法》的壹傳媒集團主席黎智英，以現金1000萬元保釋候訊，書面理由將於明天下午4時半頒布。律政司就保釋決定上訴至終審法院，將於本月31日開庭處理。( 全文）<br />\n<br />\n#20201228新聞"},{"pid":"75620f920c02114eda33061ae2b85890354724d5","tid":2343600,"uid":27122,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-12-28T05:25:55.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"95234c097275fbc72310e8a408f5fe12d4307405","tid":2343600,"uid":284432,"like":4,"dislike":0,"score":4,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-12-28T05:26:40.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},{"pid":"5bb7853c4e93051133245493f2cdcc7c390a8cd8","tid":2343600,"uid":160592,"like":14,"dislike":0,"score":14,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-12-28T05:26:53.000Z","msg":"情況同監警會搵國際專家寫報告一樣<br />\n人又係你搵，唔岩聽又換人，咁即係人治啦<img src=\"/assets/faces/xm/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"006cde95b57a4493d8fc235970c565544862be94","tid":2343600,"uid":27122,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-12-28T05:27:02.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" cla